### Hadith 3:296

*Narrated Hakim bin Hizam:*

The Prophet aid, "The buyer and the seller have the option to cancel or
to confirm the deal, as long as they have not parted or till they part,
and if they spoke the truth and told each other the defects of the
things, then blessings would be in their deal, and if they hid something
and told lies, the blessing of the deal would be lost."

